{"tid":1083160,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"19/20 NON-JUPAS 專區（20）漫漫長路是如何走過","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T18:39:57.000Z","uid":89802,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"38e3203cb6a8d3426bcd714a6ca2ff47ff94b3bd","tid":1083160,"uid":89802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"新一年Database已經預先整定左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , <br />\n到左十一月,十二月就差唔多會收到interview/offer, <br />\n屆時巴絲可以填呢張form分享消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後祝大家收到心儀offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年一度既non-jupas又到了, 巴絲們都可能收到Offer / Interview通知, 希望你們可以提供呢啲資訊造福下年師弟師妹,<br />\n即使有interview冇offer都希望你地留低啲有用既資料, 俾大家作為參考<br />\n多謝你地既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019-2020 Non-JUPAS 資料庫<br />\n填Offer：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/5UdnN3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F5UdnN3&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=d7354aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/5UdnN3</a><br />\n<br />\n睇Offer：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/hoyVm1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhoyVm1&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=98b899b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/hoyVm1</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲你地好 歡迎各位想申請Non - JUPAS / 副學士過來人分享經驗<br />\n<br />\n本Post會繼續為各位想了解asso的巴打/絲打提供援助<br />\n如果想到舊Post爬文, 各位可以於高登或Google Search以下字眼:<br />\n<br />\n1. Associate Degree 副學士專區<br />\n2. Associate Degree 副學士咨詢區<br />\n3. Non-JUPAS 交流區 有用資訊:<br />\n<br />\nHKCC官網: 已轉換文字為連結<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkcc-polyu.edu.hk\" data-sr-u